  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span dir=\"ltr\">A small sphere the size of a golf ball that when thrown against a solid surface, explodes into a Thick red mist up to 10 feet high and 5 feet wide before dissipating within 1 minute.</span></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\"> When used creates a hazy red fog that doesn't obscure vision, but causes a direct nasal stimulation to creatures in its radius.</span></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\"> All creatures in the affected area who begins its turn in the mist, can remake any saving throw to resist or end a genjutsu at the beginning of their turns, regardless of the effects of the genjutsu itself.</span></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\"> A creature can only gain the benefit of this item twice per use.</span></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\">Grants Advantage on Genjutsu Saves.</span></p>",
